title: [Ta'Vaalor Dye Wares, Main Room]
description: Smoothly polished oak walls reflect soft light from the high ceiling's chandelier.  A long table stretches across the front wall.  Several barrels sit at the end of the table, opposite of the door.  A series of oak pedestals stands in the center of the room, highlighting several pieces of merchandise.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, west, out
